olspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\"|\n|[[Sanjay Mishra (actor)|Sanjay Mishra]]\n|-\n! Prem's sister in law\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\"|\n|[[Kangna Sharma]]\n|-\n! Meet's brother in law\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\"|\n|[[Ketan Karande]]\n|-\n! Babu Rangeela\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\"|\n|[[Shreyas Talpade]]\n|-\n! Shiney\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\"|\n|[[Sonali Raut]]\n|-\n! Ramsey\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\"|\n|[[Sudesh Lehri]]\n|-\n|}\n\n==Crew==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\" width=\"100%\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Occupation\n! colspan=\"4\" | Film\n|-\n!  width:10%;\"| ''[[Masti (2004 film)|Masti]]'' <br>(2004)\n!  width:10%;\"| ''[[Grand Masti]]'' <br>(2013)\n!  width:10%;\"| ''[[Great Grand Masti]]'' <br>(2016)\n|-\n! Director\n| colspan=\"3\" | [[Indra Kumar]]\n|-\n! Producer(s)\n| Ashok Thakeria\n| Ashok Thakeria<br>[[Indra Kumar]]\n| Ashok Thakeria<br>[[Ekta Kapoor]]<br>[[Shobha Kapoor]]\n|-\n! Writer(s)\n| [[Bhavani Iyer]]<br>[[Indra Kumar]]\n| [[Milap Zaveri]]<br>Tushar Hiranandani <br>[[Indra Kumar]]\n| Tushar Hiranandani\n|-\n! Composer(s)\n| [[Anand Raj Anand]]\n| [[Anand Raj Anand]]<br>[[Sanjeev Darshan]]\n| Sanjeev Darshan, Shaarib&Toshi, Shaan\n|-\n! Director of photography\n| [[Mazhar Kamran]]\n| Rituraj Narain\n| Nigam Bomzan\n|-\n! Editor(s)\n| colspan=\"3\" | Sanjay Sankla\n|}\n\n==Release and revenue==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:centr;\"| Film\n! style=\"text-align:centr;\"| Release date\n! style=\"text-align:centr;\"| Budget\n! style=\"text-align:centr;\"| Box office revenue\n|-\n| ''[[Masti (2004 film)|Masti]]'' ||  9 April 2004 || {{INRConvert|5|c}} || {{INRConvert|26.8|c}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Box Office 2004|url=http://www.boxofficeindia.com/showProd.php?itemCat=210&catName=MjAwNA==|publisher=Boxofficeindia.com|accessdate=6 February 2015|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.ar